name: VR plasticity exploration 1
description: VR plasticity exploration 1 is the first piece in series of images and 3D models that are capturing an individual path of finding an artistic language and style of the artist. This 3D object is made by Nikita Khudiakov in March 2021 and captured as image. More info about the artists can be found here - https://linktr.ee/voobrazhenie
